  <name>W-Engine Pro</name>
  <summary>Advanced wallpaper engine for Linux with video and interactive support</summary>
  <description>
    <p>W-Engine Pro is a powerful wallpaper engine that supports:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Video wallpapers with mpv backend</li>
      <li>Parallax and web-based wallpapers</li>
      <li>X11 and Wayland (including GNOME) support</li>
      <li>System monitoring overlays</li>
      <li>Plugin system and theme customization</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
